content: That's really helpful, thanks! I think I'll start with a lower price point and see how it goes. By the way, I recently moved into a new apartment and finally had the chance to unpack my art collection, including the painting "Sunset" by an up-and-coming artist I met at an art fair in Brooklyn last October. I remember attending the fair with my friend Emma, and we ended up buying a few pieces from emerging artists. The "Sunset" painting is one of my favorites, and it looks great in my new living room.
